body_html:
Did you have NVIDA GPU on your Mac?
If not then don't use the CUDA version of the tensor flow.
Uninstall tensor flow and reinstall the CPU version of the tensor flow you will be able to bypass the error.

Did you have NVIDA GPU on your Mac?
If not then don't use the CUDA version of the tensor flow.
